  "prompt": "When is next Quora meetup in Mumbai?",
  "response": "As of my knowledge cutoff in October 2023, I don't have specific information about upcoming Quora meetups in Mumbai. To find the most accurate and up-to-date details, I recommend the following steps:\n\n1. **Visit Quora's Official Website:** Check the [Quora Events](https://www.quora.com/events) page, if available, for any announcements regarding meetups or events in Mumbai.\n\n2. **Follow Quora on Social Media:** Quora often shares event information on their official social media channels such as [Twitter](https://twitter.com/quora), [Facebook](https://www.facebook.com/quora), or [LinkedIn](https://www.linkedin.com/company/quora).\n\n3. **Check Community Forums:** Sometimes, local community forums or Quora's own community spaces may have information about upcoming meetups.\n\n4. **Subscribe to Newsletters:** If Quora offers a newsletter or mailing list, subscribing to it can ensure you receive updates about events and meetups directly in your inbox.\n\n5. **Contact Quora Support:** If you're unable to find the information online, consider reaching out to Quora's support team for assistance.\n\nKeep an eye on these channels for the latest information regarding Quora meetups in Mumbai or other locations.",
